<br>
You didn't mention what you were previously wearing in your belt/back slot so I will just go out on a limb here...<br>
<br>
If you like the haste on the gaunts and want to improve the ac/etc... on your belt/back slots to compensate for the lost ac from using your SS gaunts you might look into:<br>
<br>
Axgaroth's Belt of Defense - 20ac 15str 15wis -- drops in Maidens Eye off the Xin Thall Centiens (seems to be rare drop now)<br>
<br>
Cloak of the Maelstrom - 20ish ac + other stuff (don't remember) Kael quest but I don't believe it is no-drop and there for purchaseable<br>
<br>
Seahorse Spine Cloak (may be totally butchering the name) - 20ish ac .. drops in SG and is a pretty nice cloak<br>
<br>
